Author: Jekwizor
Title: [ANN] MIX.Rent Decentralized platform TO RENT AND SHARE VEHICLES.
Body: Mixrent Partners with PumaPay to accept Recurring Payments   Limassol, Cyprus, October 31, 2018: Today, PumaPay, the open source blockchain-based billing protocol, announced its partnership with Mixrent, a blockchain-based ecosystem that connects travelers with transport owners worldwide.  PumaPay’s PullPayment Protocol will be adopted by Mixrent, which will offer its customers PumaPay’s flexible crypto-payment solution, including recurring payments.  PumaPay’s innovative blockchain payment solution is designed to make financial transactions faster, easier and cost-efficient, and offers a viable long-term alternative to the use of traditional credit cards. With transactions processed in real time, there are no chargebacks or delays for merchants. PumaPay’s billing architecture seeks to build a stronger connection between merchants and their customers by enabling flexible payment scenarios tailored to meet the needs of both businesses and their users.  With Version 2 of the solution, customers will have the option to decide among three billing models, including recurring payments which are now available on the Testnet.  https://pumapay.io/mixrent-partners-pumapay-recurring-payments/
